 2024 Toyota Land Cruiser https://ritholtz.com/2023/08/2024-toyota-land-cruiser/Admin Tim Sun, 06 Aug 2023 15:16:18 +0000 CarsWeekend https://ritholtz.com/?p=317703 <p> Since the Land Cruiser was first introduced in the 1950s for Japan&#39;s Army, Toyota has sold more than 11.3 million of the rugged, offroaders globally. The truck has proven itself a favorite. Its simple but rugged and reliable mechanicals is why it&#39;s a favorite of everyone that traverses desserts, glaciers, mountains and other rough terrain.…</p><p> <a class="button" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/08/2024-toyota-land-cruiser/">Read More<i class="icon ion-arrow-right-c"></i></a></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/08/2024-toyota-land-cruiser/">2024 Toyota Land Cruiser</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">The Big Picture</a> .</p> ; <p> Since the Land Cruiser was first introduced in the 1950s for Japan&#39;s Army, Toyota has sold more than 11.3 million of the rugged, offroaders globally.</p><p> The truck has proven itself a favorite. Its simple but rugged and reliable mechanicals is why it&#39;s a favorite of everyone that traverses desserts, glaciers, mountains and other rough terrain. Land Cruiser is Toyota&#39;s longest-running nameplate, ostensibly a nod to Britain&#39;s Land Rover. (Note the special edition with the round headlights looks like a nod to the latest Defender).</p><p> The new version is coming to America in Spring 2024, giving Jeep and Bronco enthusiasts a third option.</p><p> The specs are impressive:</p><blockquote><p> Powertrain: Hybrid four-cylinder<br /> Gas engine: Turbocharged 2.4-liter 4<br /> Hybrid: 2 electric motors<br /> 4WD: four-wheel drive system with low-range + locking differential<br /> Total Power: 326 horsepower + 465 lb.-ft. of torque.<br /> 2-row, 5-seat SUV<br /> Towing Capacity: 6,000 lbs.<br /> Price: starts in the mid-$50,000 range.</p></blockquote><p> It&#39;s a good-looking albeit boxy rig. At the new price point with its well-established reputation for legendary toughness and durability, I expect it will find a receptive audience in the States.</p><p></p><p></p><p> <em>Previously</em> :<br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/2021/10/1974-toyota-fj40/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1978 Toyota FJ40</a> (October 29, 2021)</p><p></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317704" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="404" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1.jpeg 1200w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-1024x575.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-768x431.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/1-250x140.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317712" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="480" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1.jpeg 980w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2-1-250x167.jpeg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-317705" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="480" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3.jpeg 980w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/3-300x200